review_blob: Too unique to be only defined as "oatmeal porter". Growing and becoming better and better. Dark, almost black.A mouth-caressing beer. High drinkable due its ballancaed body,A+!
Black with red reflections, great head. Addictive taste, never boring. Ballanced hops and roast,with a sweet caress. Probably one of the best companions in long winter nights.
